channel.title: How to remove and add fishing spots! please help~!
channel.description: i am currently working on devolution 7.0 source. and at catherby the fishing spots are messed, what file do i add and remove fishing spots? thanks.

item.title: How to remove and add fishing spots! please help~!
item.dc:creator: @southpaw63 southpaw63
item.description:
@southpaw63 wrote:

Find the coords for fishing spots you want to take out. Search for those coords in autospawn.cfg. Delete the whole line containing info on the fishing spots you want deleted.

To add, do the same thing, bit this time insert the information into autospawn.cfg.

Hope this helped.
